## Critical Workflow Rules

### ALWAYS
- ✅ Read rule files directly from disk
- ✅ Write rule changes directly to files
- ✅ Verify file changes after writing
- ✅ Use file system tools, not cache

### NEVER
- ❌ Rely on Cursor's rules cache
- ❌ Assume rules are available without reading files
- ❌ Skip verification of file changes
- ❌ Use cached rule content for decisions

